# and not a join.
query T multiline
explain plan for select b, c from foo, (select 5 as a) const where foo.a = const.a
----
Source materialize.public.foo (u1):
| Filter (#0 = 5)
| Project (#0..=#2)

Query:
%0 =
| Get materialize.public.foo (u1)
| Filter (#0 = 5)
| Project (#1, #2)

EOF

query TR
